
 Twitch is an American video live streaming service that focuses on video game live streaming, including broadcasts of esports competitions, in addition to offering music broadcasts, creative content, and "in real life" streams.


 This is an automation software that can convert text to speech. The text come from the viewers using special message in Twitch chat  
 The special message can only be used by a point that you earn by watching the stream 





version 1.3
  open only chat 
    url = "https://www.twitch.tv/popout/{}/chat?popout=".format("twitch user name")
  use another library, and stop using selenium
  add thread < main class , second class >
  add sound if someone use channel points
  change the text under settings
  





thread = threading.Thread(target=thread_class)
thread.start()
tttt = thread_class.text
print(tttt)

